</desc></rtept><rtept lat="51.3280680" lon="-0.9291300"><ele>62.4</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3268420" lon="-0.9278830"><ele>66.1</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3257970" lon="-0.9272480"><ele>66.1</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3241750" lon="-0.9256550"><ele>66.2</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3227760" lon="-0.9237060"><ele>68.2</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3221260" lon="-0.9218370"><ele>65.8</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3213800" lon="-0.9205570"><ele>65.9</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3207290" lon="-0.9202090"><ele>66.6</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3195480" lon="-0.9201920"><ele>66.6</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3192660" lon="-0.9198000"><ele>68.5</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3191570" lon="-0.9187300"><ele>69.5</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3189660" lon="-0.9179110"><ele>71.3</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3185150" lon="-0.9165800"><ele>72</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3182172" lon="-0.9150558"><ele>77.1</ele><name>Tarmac track</name><desc>follow track and cross main road - then through to Hazeley Bottom</desc></rtept><rtept lat="51.3176411" lon="-0.9153078"><ele>79.1</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3166850" lon="-0.9150980"><ele>80</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3155350" lon="-0.9152496"><ele>85</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3151620" lon="-0.9148980"><ele>85.3</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3149930" lon="-0.9148540"><ele>85.3</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3147540" lon="-0.9164040"><ele>86.5</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3148080" lon="-0.9189540"><ele>81.9</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3146500" lon="-0.9195640"><ele>76.1</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3152490" lon="-0.9239160"><ele>64.1</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3151890" lon="-0.9255090"><ele>65.6</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3151110" lon="-0.9259680"><ele>65.6</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3157750" lon="-0.9282660"><ele>62.4</ele><name>Country Lanes to Murrell Green</name><desc>Continue along these minor roads for a few miles </desc></rtept><rtept lat="51.3144960" lon="-0.9286750"><ele>60.1</ele></rtept><rtept lat="51.3138380" lon="-0.9286750"><ele>57.9</ele